    <j.0:comment xml:lang="en">The Commission accepts the following amendments: 2, 3, 7, 16, 18, 19, 20, 21, 22, 24, 25, 26, 27, 28, 29, 30, 34, 36, 37, 40, 42, 44, 46, 48, 50. The following amendments are acceptable in spirit but need to be revised: 6, 8, 10, 17, 23, 31, 35, 39, 52, 58. The Commission cannot accept the following amendments: 4, 5, 11, 12 (except drafting amendments).</j.0:comment>
